first:
please read the instructions on https://github.com/DiKorsch/mothseg

second:
you should start your Anaconda environment with the installation of mothseg
change the directory to the main.py script in the mothseg folder
execute LepyLoop's LLmain.py by executing "python3 /path/to/LLmain.py
  youll be asked for an input directoy. please state the directory that contains the images to be analysed
  individual counts is a number, how many individiduals will be analysed in each Lepy iteration. If you experience issues on your machine, try a low number
